Class LtedManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.compassto.sixthsense.sdk.manager.LtedManager

  • public class LtedManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Central instance that builds connection to QDiscovery SDK. Initializes QDiscovery Lted Service. Executes, cancels, updates Expressions of any TransactionType
